.TH lingmo-editor 1  "2020-11-17" "Lingmo"
.SH NAME
lingmo-editor \- the Text editor from UOS
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lingmo-editor
[\fIPATH\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Text editor for OCEAN (Lingmo Desktop Environment).
.PP
This program does not accept any command line options.
If the \fIPATH\fR is specified, open that file with .
If the \fIPATH\fR is omitted, open lingmo-editor and show nothing.
If lingmo-editor has been launched, open the Text with lingmo-editor. 
Otherwise, launch lingmo-editor and open the Text with it.
.SH SEE ALSO
https://www.lingmo.org/en/original/lingmo-editor/
